tion q(n), it\ngives an affine-invariant property that is testable with O(q(n))-queries, but\nnot with o(q(n))-queries, complementing an analogous result of [GKNR09] for\ngraph properties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 4 Oct 2009 21:17:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 9 Apr 2010 05:06:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-04-12"}
