ed on G; and several reasoning examples which demonstrate the\nexpressiveness and naturalness of both G and Abella.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Oct 2009 12:36:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 Oct 2009 20:06:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-06"}
